data.description: Location! Location!! Location!!! BERMUDA BAY Subdivision just South of Hunters creek near everything, water view home. Good for first time home buyer and great for investment., just off John young parkway beautiful three-bedroom and two-bathroom cozy house., vaulted ceiling, lot of windows with light with water view. separate kitchen and breakfast nook spacious living and dining room, slide glass door to huge, covered porch facing pond. it's a quiet neighborhood with community swimming pool next door to enjoy, walking pathway around pond just few steps away and more. New water heater, well maintained HVAC, ceramic tile and carpet flooring throughout one can enjoy. LOOP shopping, best schools, restaurants, hospital all central Florida attractions are minutes way., Major highway access nearby to enjoy Florida beaches.
